      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0632P0-02644'>
        <a name='S5LV0632P0_20020313_GCR_72'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-rachel-gardner' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0632P0_20020313_GCR_72' title='Link to this speech by Ms Rachel Gardner' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-rachel-gardner" title="Ms Rachel Gardner">Baroness Gardner of Parkes</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            When I used to sit on an industrial tribunal, it was a regular discussion as to whether the word "normal" included overtime and whether it only included overtime if you were obliged to do it as opposed to it being voluntary. The same complication comes in with the word "average". These are points that should be clarified.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0632P0-02645'>
        <a name='S5LV0632P0_20020313_GCR_73'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-sainsbury' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0632P0_20020313_GCR_73' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Sainsbury' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
