      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0632P0-02686'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0632P0_20020313_GCR_114' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 12 [Penalties: fraud etc]:
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0632P0-02687'>
        <a name='S5LV0632P0_20020313_GCR_115'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-edward-razzall' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
